        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MechaX｜About-Us"><a href="#MechaX｜About-Us" class="headerlink" title="MechaX｜About Us"></a>MechaX｜About Us</h1><hr><p>Introduction to team MechaX in Chongqing University</p><h2 id="Who-Are-We"><a href="#Who-Are-We" class="headerlink" title="Who Are We?"></a>Who Are We?</h2><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=112884977894219&bvid=BV1VFvaeoE8Q&cid=500001634419610&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>MechaX is a robot team established on the basis of the X-Innovation Center of Chongqing University. Its members are undergraduates majoring in mechanics, electrical information, and automation.]]></content>
      
      
      
